{"contents":[{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"H1","content":"UNIT 02 面试话题 Interview Topics"},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"H2","content":"Lesson 1 个人信息 Personal Information"},{"imgSrc":["https://res.weread.qq.com/wrepub/epub_26796696_168"],"tagName":"DIV","content":""},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":"场景对话"},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":""},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":"杰克在参加一场面试，面试官史密斯先生在询问杰克一些个人信息。"},{"title":"杰克：史密斯先生您好，很高兴见到您。","answer":"Jack: Hello, Mr. Smith, nice to meet you.","describe":null},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":""},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":""},{"title":"杰克：我感到很荣幸。","answer":"Jack: I feel very honored.","describe":null},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":""},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"DIV","content":"    职场达人小技巧    面试之自我介绍    求职者在参加面试时，要经历的第一个环节就是做自我介绍。所谓自我介绍就是求职者向面试官介绍自己的情况，让面试官对其有一个初步的认识和了解。在做自我介绍时，一般应从基本的个人信息开始。"},{"title":"杰克：您请讲。","answer":"Jack: Please.","describe":null},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":""},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":""},{"title":"杰克：我今年23岁。","answer":"Jack: I am twenty-three years old.","describe":null},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":""},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":""},{"title":"杰克：我住在离这儿不远的一个小区里。","answer":"Jack: I live in a sub-district near here.","describe":null},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":""},{"imgSrc":["https://res.weread.qq.com/wrepub/epub_26796696_174"],"tagName":"DIV","content":""},{"title":"杰克：我的电话号码是1033-5768。","answer":"Jack: My telephone number is 1033-5768.","describe":null},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":""},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":""},{"title":"杰克：是的，我出生在北京。","answer":"Jack: Yes, I was born in Bei jing.","describe":null},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":""},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"DIV","content":"    在向面试官介绍自己的个人信息时，应清楚地说明自己的姓名（如果面试需要，还要说出自己的英文名）、年龄、毕业学校；其次，谈一下自己的专业和特长；最后，根据面试的具体情况，可以有选择性的谈一下自己的经历、家庭状况等。"},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":"必背例句"},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":"1.Let me introduce myself first．先让我做一下自我介绍。"},{"title":"我的名字叫李明。","answer":"My name is Li Ming．","describe":null},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":"3.My present address is 115 Jiankang Road．我现在的住址是健康路115号。"},{"title":"我出生于1988年3月9日。","answer":"I was born on March 9th, 1988．","describe":null},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":"5.My English name is Tony．我的英文名字叫托尼。"},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":"6.I am not married yet. I am still single ."},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":"我还没有结婚，现在仍然单身。"},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":"7.I live with my friend now．我现在和我的朋友一起住。"},{"title":"我是汉族人。","answer":"My nationality is Han．","describe":null},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":"9.Do you have an alias？你有别名吗？"},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":"10.My pen name is Mengzhongren (The person in the dream)."},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":"我的笔名叫梦中人。"},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"DIV","content":"    虽然个人信息比较简单，但是内容涵盖比较繁琐，在面试时一定要有条理地告诉给面试官，不可东说一句，西凑一句，以免给面试者留下逻辑性不强的印象。"},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":""},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":"核心词汇总"},{"word":"subject","yinbiao":"['sʌbdʒikt]","hanyi":"n. 话题，主题"},{"word":"honor","yinbiao":"['ɔnə]","hanyi":"n. 荣誉，荣幸"},{"word":"subdistrict","yinbiao":"['sʌbdistrikt]","hanyi":"n. 小区，住宅区"},{"word":"present","yinbiao":"['preznt]","hanyi":"adj. 现在的"},{"word":"permanent","yinbiao":"['pə:mənənt]","hanyi":"adj. 长久的"},{"word":"temporary","yinbiao":"['tempəreri]","hanyi":"adj. 暂时的"},{"word":"address","yinbiao":"['ædres]","hanyi":"[ə'dres] n. 住址，地址"},{"word":"birth","yinbiao":"[bə:θ]","hanyi":"n. 出生"},{"word":"birthday","yinbiao":"['bə:θdei]","hanyi":"n. 生日"},{"word":"birthplace","yinbiao":"['bə:θpleis]","hanyi":"n. 出生地"},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":"birth date 出生日期"},{"word":"marry","yinbiao":"['mæri]","hanyi":"v. 结婚"},{"word":"single","yinbiao":"['siŋgl]","hanyi":"adj. 单身的"},{"word":"alias","yinbiao":"['eiliæs]","hanyi":"n. 别名"},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":"pen name 笔名"},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":"full name 全名"},{"imgSrc":[],"tagName":"P","content":"family name 姓氏"},{"word":"surname","yinbiao":"['sə:neim]","hanyi":"n. 姓"},{"word":"province","yinbiao":"['prɔvins]","hanyi":"n. 省"},{"word":"city","yinbiao":"['siti]","hanyi":"n. 城市"}]}